room_title: Escape room "The Spell" by Talon Falls Escape in Paducah
room_description: Witches and vampires have been at war for ages. The coven has been trying to put the last vampire to death. They put him under a spell for 200 years before perishing in an attempt to finally end the war. You've been chosen to seek out the vampire's eternal resting place and stake him before he wakes.
